'This is something I'm very uncomfortable showing,' he admits in the video. 'I don't go out in public like this, and I haven't gone swimming in over a decade because I'm too ashamed really.'

Mr Flemming says his rib cage sticks out as a result of it expanding to push his former weight away from his organs.

